    "In this section, we describe the algorithm for computing the Fourier transform of Stokes data in the class of cases we are interested in here.",
    "It is based on the results of [Moc25], but we (re)formulate it in the language of Stokes local systems, so that it yields in particular isomorphisms between wild character varieties.",
